**Our Strategic Approach:**
Organise by distinct coastal aesthetics — each H2 a mood, not a design type. Give honest intel on durability within each category. Answer the active-holiday vs photoshoot tradeoff directly. Make short nails feel fully included. This is the edit that helps a reader choose, not just browse.

